  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbb\u0db9 \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0 \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dda \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9d\u0ddd\u0dc2\u0dab",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protests in Galle against Mataramba Cotton",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of civil organizations and public activists engaged in a silent demonstration today (23rd) in front of the Galle court complex saying \"Let's oppose child abuse\".",
        "The protest was held at the time the suspect named Keerthi Kumara Batagoda, who is accused of abusing a large number of school-aged boys while running a place called Mataramba Satara Maha Devalaya in Galle, was brought to court in Galle today (23rd).",
        "A large number of people including members of civil organizations participated in this protest.",
        "They demand that the police should protect the abused children instead of protecting the accused Kapua. They also demand that the law be enforced against the authorities who protect child abusers.",
        "The agitators further mentioned that even top police officers have been assigned to protect this suspect. They also mentioned that there are cases where high police officers stand up for people who abuse children, abuse and persecute women, not only in Galle but all over Sri Lanka, so they should stand against such actions."
      ],
